3D Modeler


This directory contains source code for a polygon based 3D modeling 
program.  The supported shapes are rectangular solids, cylinders, and 
a right angle prism.  Consult the file "modeler.c" for the format of the 
object description file.  The included files are:

	modeler.c	- main program
	modlutls.h	- primitive generation functions
	unitutls.h	- unit sized primitive functions
	mathutls.h	- math related functions
	object 		- sample object decription file
	data.exp	- expected data output file
	makefile	- makefile for above

Brian Lingard
March 1995

